#Government Cyber Security Strategy

The Government Cyber Security Strategy (GCSS) will be introduced on 25 January 2022. 

The GCSS is a world-leading strategy which will provide insights on how to build a cyber resilient public sector and enable the UK government to “defend as one”. 

You can watch the launch event on this page starting from 11:30 to 15:00. You should have received the password in your email invite. 

If you'd like to ask the panel a question, you can use the chat function below the video. 

If you are having trouble accessing the live stream you can email: governmentsecurity@cabinetoffice.gov.uk


